---
// The one signature dark moment in the home page rhythm. Full-bleed
// real-photo background, dark overlay for legibility, giant ultra-light
// "UNPLUG" type. Per Black Tomato's "Footsteps sub-brand panel" — the
// page-turn moment that interrupts the editorial rhythm.
---

<section class="relative bg-primary text-ink overflow-hidden">
  <img
    src="/img/source/hero/05-caribbean-night-moonlit.jpg"
    alt=""
    loading="lazy"
    decoding="async"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-50"
  />
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(15,15,15,0.65) 0%, rgba(15,15,15,0.92) 70%);"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-7 lg:px-14 py-32 sm:py-44 lg:py-56 text-center">
    <p class="font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[0.625rem] font-semibold text-ink/65 mb-8">
      The point of all of this
    </p>
    <h2
      class="font-display text-ink font-extralight leading-[0.85] tracking-[-0.05em]"
      style="font-size: clamp(4.5rem, 18vw, 16rem); font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 30, 'WONK' 0;"
    >
      UNPLUG
    </h2>
    <p
      class="font-serif-quote italic mt-10 lg:mt-14 text-[1.375rem] lg:text-[1.625rem] leading-[1.45] tracking-[-0.015em] text-ink/85 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-balance"
      style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36, 'SOFT' 60, 'WONK' 1;"
    >
      The life you've been putting off — it starts the moment the lines come off the dock.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-14 lg:mt-16">
      <a
        href="/calendar"
        class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-ink border-b-2 border-sun pb-1 hover:text-sun transition-colors"
      >
        Find Your Week
        <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="size-3 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M1 8h13M9 3l5 5-5 5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
